text: Intel Core i9 10900K is a processor that was made by Intel. It has 10 cores and 3.7 GHz clock speed, which can be boosted to 5.3 GHz. It has 20 MB cache. It was released in second quarter of 2020. == References == Category:Intel Core processors Category:Processors released in 2020s Category:Multi-core processors
